html:
{%- from "templates/print_formats/standard_macros.html" import render_field with context -%}
{%- macro add_header(page_num, max_pages, doc, letter_head, no_letterhead, footer, print_settings=None) -%}
{% if letter_head and not no_letterhead%}
    <div class="letter-head">{{ letter_head }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if doc.print_heading_template %}
    {{ ducky.render_template(doc.print_heading_template, {"doc":doc})}}
    {% else %}
    {% endif %} {%- endmacro -%} {% for page in layout %}
        <div {% if print_settings.repeat_header_footer %} id="header-html" class="hidden-pdf" {% endif %}>
            {{ add_header(loop.index, layout|len, doc, letter_head, no_letterhead, footer, print_settings) }}
        </div>
        {% if print_settings.repeat_header_footer %}
        <div id="footer-html" class="visible-pdf">
            {% if not no_letterhead and footer %}
            <div class="letter-head-footer custom-aht-footer">{{ footer }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="text-center xsall page-number visible-pdf">
                {{ _("Page {0} of {1}").format('<span class="page"></span>', '<span class="topage"></span>') }}
            </p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
<h2 style="text-align:center;">EMPLOYMENT CERTIFICATE</h2>
<div style="text-align: right; margin-bottom:15px;">Date: {{ frappe.utils.getdate() }}</div>
<div style="margin-bottom:15px;">
<p>To,</p>
<p>The Embassy of {{ doc.custom_country }}</p>
<p>Doha – Qatar</p>
</div>
<div style="margin-top:15px; line-height:1.8;">
<p style="text-align:center"><u>TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN</u></p>
<br>
<p>This is to certify that {{ doc.salutation }} {{ doc.employee_name }}, QID No: {{ doc.custom_qid_number }}, Passport No: {{ doc.passport_number }} is
working with our reputed company as {{ doc.designation }}. {{ doc.salutation }} has been working with us
since {{ doc.date_of_joining }} and proved to be a very dedicated resource who has
been very loyal to the company. {{ 'His' if doc.salutation == 'Mr' else 'Her' }} total amount of remuneration is {{ doc.salary_currency }} {{ doc.ctc }}/-per
month.</p>
<br>
<p>
    {{ doc.salutation }} {{ doc.employee_name }} is scheduled to travel from {{ doc.from_date }} to
    {{ doc.to_date }} during {{ 'his' if doc.salutation == 'Mr' else 'her' }} approved vacation period. Our company has no
    objection to {{ 'his' if doc.salutation == 'Mr' else 'her' }} travel or visa application.
</p>
<br>
<p>We are issuing this letter on the request of our employee and do not hold any liability
on behalf of this letter and does not in any way hold itself responsible for any
consequences arising out of this letter.</p>
</div>
<br><br>
{%- if doc.company == 'Zajel' -%}
<p style="margin-top: 20px;">For {{ doc.company }} Marketing</p>
{%- else -%}
<p style="margin-top: 20px;">For {{ doc.company }}</p>
{%- endif -%}
<br><br>
{%- if doc.company == 'Velo' -%}
<p>Abdulla Al-Kuwari</p>
<p>Managing Director</p>
{%- else -%}
<p>Ali Al-Kuwari</p>
<p>Chief Executive Officer</p>
{% if doc.status == "Approved" and doc.valid_till and doc.valid_till >= frappe.utils.today() and not frappe.form_dict.get("preview") %}
<p style="margin-top: 3%; width: 29%;"><img src="https://tabrah-holding.frappe.cloud/files/Ali%20Signature.svg"></p>
{%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
</div>
    </div>
{%- endfor -%}
